    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 9th level, you can draw a random harrow card from a complete harrow deck you own as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>&nbsp;and channel the aspects of the card into your body. You take on superficial traits featured on the card and gain a +4&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Enhancement-Bonus\">enhancement bonus</a>&nbsp;to the ability score associated with the cardâ€™s suit. You can invoke the harrow for a number of minutes per day equal to your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;level; the duration need not be continuous, but it must be used in 1-minute increments.</p>",
